title: California wants to protect indoor workers from heat. That goal is now in limbo
description: The state was on the cusp of making new rules to protect people who work in places like warehouses from dangerous heat. A last-minute shake-up leaves workers wondering if they'll be safe come summer.

title: Like a Phish concert but with more grievance, this is what it's like at a Trump rally
description: Many Americans won't experience a rally for former President Donald Trump in person, instead witnessing these events through viral clips. But for the faithful, a Trump rally is so much more than that.

title: Tierra Whack opens up: 'Don't we all fake it?'
description: The success of the polymath's technicolor Whack World EP left something darker brewing beneath the surface. Years later, she talks about pushing through self-doubt to rediscover her confidence.
